          "reviewBody": "Worst school for education and bad atmosphere, too much Ego in all staff members and Admin and account team is not at all courteous. My son studied for 8 years in this school but removed later as they don't listen to parents and education is old school types with 15-20 KG bags and every week exams, too much burden on student and parent .",
