            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I went there for my kids’ admission in LKG, he took the test. I was also there and my child did extremely well, I have no clue what did they expect out of a child who is just in Nursery and struggling to get into LKG. They sent out an email saying the child has to appear for a retest.\nI was shocked to see the mail that even after doing so well that even I wasn’t expecting he will do, then also they were not satisfied rather sent us saying he has to come for a retest.\nMeanwhile, he got admission in other school.\nI am simply wondering if he is taking any IAS exam that we need to appear multiple times.\n\nPathetic staff and specially the headmistress ‘Shivani’.\nSo rude and full of attitude. I feel pity for her.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
